{"tid":1549189,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"不要說: \"你跌咗個良心呀!\"。試著說: \"你跌咗個正義感呀!\"","createTime":"2019-09-07T08:43:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T09:13:10.000Z","uid":284284,"like":3,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d2079d722d0653db585bef89a2833018efdfad4c","tid":1549189,"uid":284284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T08:43:17.000Z","msg":"不要說: &quot;你跌咗個良心呀&quot;<br />\n試著說: &quot;你跌咗個正義感呀&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;良心&quot; 呢個字，太過複雜喇<br />\n就好似個 &quot;愛&quot; 字一樣<br />\n冇絕對嘅定義<br />\n愛自由愛民主，又係愛<br />\n愛黨愛國，又係愛 (or at least 為自己係)<br />\n乜野人睇到乜野<br />\n<br />\n佢哋宣誓嘅時候<br />\n洗唔洗話自己係一個有良心嘅人？我相信唔需要<br />\n而且法律上應該係冇&quot;良心&quot;嘅definition嘅<br />\n<br />\n&quot;良心&quot; 呢個字其實同警察嘅關係唔係太大<br />\n但係&quot;正義感&quot;呢，就唔同嘞<br />\n小朋友都知道，警察應該係正義㗎嘛<br />\n如果你冇正義感，咁你就已經冇資格當差啦!<br />\n<br />\n呢個，先至係佢哋嘅痛點<br />\n<br />\n因為佢哋係宣誓過 &quot;不畏懼 不徇私&quot; 㗎嘛<br />\n正義，咪exactly就係 &quot;不畏懼 不徇私&quot; 囉<br />\n<br />\n所以，唔應該再用 &quot;你跌咗個良心呀!&quot; <br />\n應該用: &quot;你跌咗個正義感呀!&quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4d937b8aa182373225f23005e25c0d91221735b","tid":1549189,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T08:43:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bea59852d2463ffb793d8f7e732288ed5dd9ab1f","tid":1549189,"uid":706,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T08:45:27.000Z","msg":"連良心都無，仲講正義感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb276c949ace968f7f4e9c4f749fa38207b7675","tid":1549189,"uid":8219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T08:45:31.000Z","msg":"跌咩撚<br />\n2