replyTime":"2019-09-07T08:55:54.000Z","msg":"佢地本來就無 為左份糧先做狗<br />\n惻隱之心就是見人遭遇不幸，而生不忍、同情之心。 這是孟子說的一段話，他所舉的例子就是看到如果有小孩子將要溺水，每個人都會興起憐憫之心，這就是惻隱之心。 俺與你萍水相逢，出身相救，實出惻隱之心，非貪美麗之貌。 注釋：見到別人遭受不幸時心中所生的難過、同情。<br />\n連人性都無既警犬 同佢地講正義感 真係曬q氣"},{"pid":"790a89f72e820ae9a3881c4cbe119c5912e59bd9","tid":1549189,"uid":103050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T08:56:06.000Z","msg":"智障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70b7bc437ea4c5b34d18a960096a736b95291d3c","tid":1549189,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:13:10.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n針對中立淺藍黃嘅文宣【牆紙！】<br />\n<br />\n第四期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1</a><br />\n第三期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1</a><br />\n第二期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1</a><br />\n第一期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1</a><br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=59R0jsXjdYUW2Qgfgwt6uO9%2By3EgolabMfI9ImFPBT4%3D&h=4983e377\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a>"}]}